tuition's only 2%.

00:06:30.740 --> 00:06:34.860
The real rate of inflation
runs 5% or 6% right now.

00:06:34.860 --> 00:06:36.600
That's the real rate.

00:06:36.600 --> 00:06:41.590
The deficit, you'll read
a $500 billion deficit.

00:06:41.590 --> 00:06:43.360
The deficit's not $500 billion.

00:06:43.360 --> 00:06:47.150
The current deficit in the
last 12 months is $1 trillion.

00:06:47.150 --> 00:06:49.530
It's very simple to know
what the deficit is.

00:06:49.530 --> 00:06:53.520
It's the increase in government
debt over a period of time.

00:06:53.520 --> 00:06:56.730
But the way the government
keeps the statistics,

00:06:56.730 --> 00:07:00.560
their definition
of today's deficit

00:07:00.560 --> 00:07:02.900
is one half of the true deficit.

