00:08:45.310 --> 00:08:49.620
The noise-- there's never
been more noise ever

00:08:49.620 --> 00:08:52.270
in trying to make predictions,
and the reason there

00:08:52.270 --> 00:08:56.160
are so many mixed signals--
you see, the internet is great.

00:08:56.160 --> 00:08:59.630
The internet-- however, the
negative on the internet

00:08:59.630 --> 00:09:02.259
is there's way too much noise.

00:09:02.259 --> 00:09:04.050
And I was just reading
the "New York Post."

00:09:04.050 --> 00:09:05.300
I can't believe the statistic.

00:09:05.300 --> 00:09:07.160
They said the average
worker in tech

00:09:07.160 --> 00:09:12.720
and so on spends six hours
a day retrieving emails.

00:09:12.720 --> 00:09:17.990
And my son here-- who's
assistant DA at the district

00:09:17.990 --> 00:09:20.930
attorney's office, he's head
