00:40:57.450 --> 00:41:00.970
Why does Warren Buffett-- why
is he so confident there will

00:41:00.970 --> 00:41:02.940
be no change after he's gone?

00:41:02.940 --> 00:41:05.360
Because he's got Bill Gates.

00:41:05.360 --> 00:41:09.060
The lock box now goes to
Bill Gates Foundation.

00:41:09.060 --> 00:41:12.280
The foundation already
has $45 billion.

00:41:12.280 --> 00:41:14.610
Right now, with
