two thirds to already

00:41:25.260 --> 00:41:27.720
which is the largest
foundation, private foundation,

00:41:27.720 --> 00:41:28.440
in the world?

00:41:28.440 --> 00:41:31.380
The reason is you want
Bill Gates Foundation

00:41:31.380 --> 00:41:33.590
to have the voting control.

00:41:33.590 --> 00:41:35.990
Bill Gates, who is
his bridge playing

00:41:35.990 --> 00:41:39.470
partner, personal friend,
